Mark R. Widmar



Mr. Mark R. Widmar is on the Board of Directors at First Solar, Inc., 8point3 Energy Partners LP and 8point3 General Partner LLC. Mr. Widmar was previously employed as CFO & President-Engineering Solutions by GrafTech International Ltd., Controller by NCR Corp., Divisional Controller by Dell Computer Corp., Accountant by Ernst & Young LLP, a Principal by AlliedSignal, Inc., a Principal by Bristol-Myers Squibb Co., and a Principal by Lucent Technologies, Inc. He received his undergraduate degree from Indiana University and an MBA from Indiana University.



