Corporate Governance













Mark R. Widmar

Director
 
Mark Widmar is a Director on the Board of Directors of our general partner. Mr. Widmar also serves as the Chief Executive Officer of First Solar. He joined First Solar in 2011 as Chief Financial Officer and served as First Solar’s Chief Accounting Officer from February 2012 through June 2015. Previously, Mr. Widmar has served as Chief Financial Officer and President of Engineering Solutions for GraphTech International Ltd., a leading global manufacturer of advanced carbon and graphite materials. Prior to joining GraphTech, Mr. Widmar served in executive finance roles at NCR Inc., and various financial and managerial positions with Lucent Technologies, Inc., Allied Signal, Inc., and Bristol Myers/Squibb, Inc.







 
 

 
 





















